{
  "stem": "7069.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And there were served-- if they wanted [? a ?] coffee, or hot chocolate, and wonderful torte pieces.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So they, they were all, all treated to this while the delegation was there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Of course, when the delegation came home, they reported, yeah, well-- they were allowed to talk to the Danish and to Red Cross, to the prisoners, of course.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The Danish people, prisoners wouldn't dare to talk, because the Nazi uniform-- Nazi staff stood around who understood Danish.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they knew that, so they would-- could not say, say anything critical.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And so of course, Danish, as well as the Red Cross delegation, came home and said, well, while these people are confined, yes, they cannot leave this place.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But they are treated well.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The kids we see are being treated well, and so on and so forth.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And then--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They bought it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In fact, after the Red Cross visited, was the German newspapers headlined, while talking about the delegation, the Red Cross delegation that came to there, they headlined, quote, unquote, 'while, while our, while our soldiers on the front are bleeding to death, the Jews are feeding themselves on chocolate drinks and, and, and, tarts.' That was swallowed all the way along.",
      "word_count": 61
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then the following night, we had to dismantle that stuff again.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The kids were sent to the dungeons, and the old folks back to their miserable places.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, but, but you can't let it-- if you want to survive, you cannot let it consume you.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You were aware of it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But there was nothing you could do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You just put it aside.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's all there is to it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were hoping that some, maybe one of the Danes would be able to tell secretly what's really going on or something.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
